    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2005-10-07</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-11-21T20:24:45Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Community Disaster Loan Equity Act of 2005 - Amends the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act to authorize the President to make community disaster loans to state governments. Eliminates the $5 million limit on such a loan, and prohibits the President from requiring its repayment, if the state or local government receiving it may suffer a substantial loss of tax and other revenues as a result of a major disaster determined to be an incident of national significance.</p> <p></p> <p>Applies this Act to any major disaster occurring on or after August 24, 2005.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
